{"tid":939910,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢個球壇有冇人冷靜得過雲尼亞里","createTime":"2018-12-13T13:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T16:08:59.000Z","uid":165817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c657ab06a6574d1230a65f2df346afe83ee05c4d","tid":939910,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"球隊入波從來唔會大肆慶祝<br />\n輸波或者有失誤 亦都冇見過佢發脾氣屌球員<br />\n<br />\n雲加出名儒雅 都會掟下水樽 同摩佬打下交<br />\n雲尼亞里直頭冇試過大吵大鬧<br />\n冇見過佢喺鏡頭前發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一副典型慈祥老伯伯樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人感覺好有修養 好理性 好好人咁<br />\n<br />\n所以李城炒佢 咁多人戥佢可惜 一定有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ee0da8a48ab9c9f79038a0cd535b5ca352241b","tid":939910,"uid":161731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"肥賓 N76"},{"pid":"5b6366c6b3ed12bec055addee26b45be47449edf","tid":939910,"uid":67225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"08ee0da8a48ab9c9f79038a0cd535b5ca352241b","tid":939910,"uid":161731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"肥賓 N76"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"肥賓=魔術師"},{"pid":"0e650dacda01650280f025b854ecf4e4189af8b8","tid":939910,"uid":73422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"肥賓仲冷靜啦咁 入波完全無反應咁"},{"pid":"2d7e6c1194518e7e89a2f5babb6ee36f078d095b","tid":939910,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e650dacda01650280f025b854ecf4e4189af8b8","tid":939910,"uid":73422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"肥賓仲冷靜啦咁 入波完全無反應咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢長期憂鬱小生樣"}]}